Govt is scaling up mechanisation through the Belarus Facility, Bain New Holland Facility, John Deere Facility and Zoomlion Facility, alongside the upcoming Smallholder Mechanisation Facility and Post-Harvest Processing Facility, serving all categories of farmers.The model is backed by AFC Land Bank, CBZ, ZB Bank, Women’s Bank, Empower Bank, POSB and SMEDCO, boosting productivity, value addition and food security, Director in the Department of Mechanisation and Engineering, Eng Nhlanhla Magama. @obertjiri 
